dsOverview.title: ETOPO5 Global Earth Topography, 5-minute, from NGDC

summary.p: Five minute resolution global ocean depth and land surface elevation. Developed from multiple data sources and compiled by Peter Sloss at NGDC. It has been superseded by more current Terrain Elevation datasets.
